  <official_title>A Randomised, Phase 2a, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study To Evaluate The Safety, Pharmacokinetics And Antiviral Activity Of Multiple Doses Of RV521 Against Respiratory Syncytial Virus Infection In The Virus Challenge Model</official_title>
