  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main aims of the study are to assess the safety, pharmacokinetics and antiviral activity
      of multiple doses of RV521 compared to placebo in healthy adult subjects infected with
      Respiratory Syncytial Virus (RSV) in the Virus Challenge Model
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
